Detailed Description

TestRequestPacket.

After the general RequestPacket-header the format is {tabular}{rll} Position & Size & Description \ REQUEST_HEADER_SIZE & 4 bytes +4 & 4 bytes & Module nbr. +8 & 4 bytes & Server send time +12 & 4 bytes & Leader recieve time +16 & 4 bytes & Leader send/enqueue time +20 & 4 bytes & avialable reader recieve time +24 & 4 bytes & avialable reader enqueue time +28 & 4 bytes & avialable process dequeue time {tabular}
